text: Wes Cunningham (born March 9, 1987) is a Canadian professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing with the MAC Budapest in the Erste Liga. ==Playing career== Undrafted and following a season of play in Norway, Cunningham returned to North America to play the 2013–14 season in the ECHL with the Bakersfield Condors. On July 1, 2014, Cunningham was signed by Dragons de Rouen to play the 2014–15 season in the French Ligue Magnus.
